CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 12 reads: "Legal Staff - Gene Locklin, standing, clerk investigator; Atty. George W. Shields, seated left, assistant to the solicitor, and Solicitor Ralph H. Smith"
TitMainTitle: Clerk Investigator Gene Locklin, standing; Atty. George W. Shields, and Solicitor Ralph H. Smith, gathered at desk in Prothonotary's office
